name: SVR THUNDERSTORM WATCH #12
description: The S.A.N.W.S office or offices in “Jackson” and or “Hattiesburg, and Bristol” have issued a “SVR THUNDERSTORM WATCH #12” at “9:55PM EST”. primary threats to expect include “strong wind gusts up to 85MPH in some storms”. impact expect damage to “homes, businesses, vehicles, trees, outdoor objects, power lines, and outdoor animals”. this “SVR THUNDERSTORM WATCH” will expire at “7:45 PM EST” on the “2nd”.
